Linux:
    lsof -i:{portnumber}  :: displays whats a happening on said portnumber
    nohup {command} & ::  runs command in background and ignores hangup signals

Windows:
    netstat -aon  :: shows fun stuff about happening ports

CORBA naming service:
To run the project, Java Naming service needs to be started first:
tnameserv -ORBInitialPort 9888, tnameserv should be located within java jdk bin directory.
